ETHICAL USE NOTICE

This software is intended for DEFENSIVE SECURITY RESEARCH purposes only.
The framework is designed to:

1. Test LLM safety systems to identify and report vulnerabilities
2. Generate training data to improve model safety
3. Document exploitation patterns for prevention and awareness

This software should NOT be used for:

1. Actual human trafficking or labor exploitation
2. Circumventing safety systems for malicious purposes
3. Providing real guidance to bad actors

Users of this software agree to use it responsibly and ethically,
in accordance with all applicable laws and regulations.
